    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177580/extras/5ada734afc53755e0c0b2c567715eb5a.avif?t=1726919357\" width=372 height=126 /></span><br>DLC for the game <strong>Kwark</strong>!<br>In this add-on it is now possible to play with <strong>online</strong>. The game is available both in <strong>single</strong> mode and in <strong>team</strong> mode. The game can be played over <strong>WAN and LAN</strong> servers. (<i>WAN</i> - global servers to which everyone can connect | <i>LAN</i> - local servers to which you can connect only from one network).<br>In addition to playing online you get a <strong>unique skin</strong> that Kwark players don't have.<br>Skins, weapons and many interesting mechanics are waiting for you in <strong>Kwark Online</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177580/extras/9ce785ae1f80b25894463fc40e6b15df.avif?t=1726919357\" width=280 height=146 /></span>",
